What is Nova Marketplace?
Nova marketplace is a general classifieds marketplace — think housing, vehicles, electronics, appliances, anything people buy and sell locally. Sellers post listings with photos and videos, buyers browse without needing an account, and the whole thing is backed by a real API with moderation, subscriptions, and analytics behind it.
The guiding idea was to build something that actually behaves like a marketplace, not just a CRUD app with a listings table. That meant thinking through the parts most tutorials skip what a stranger can see before logging in, how sellers get discovered, how an admin keeps junk listings out, and how the business actually makes money.

