Getting noticed
Sellers can promote listings as advertisements, which show up in a featured rail on the homepage with real impression and click tracking — the groundwork for an actual ad product, not a decorative banner.
The admin side
This is the part most side projects skip entirely. Nova has a real moderation queue — admins publish or reject submitted listings with a reason, and sellers get notified either way. There’s also plan management, advertisement oversight, and a revenue dashboard that breaks down subscription income by month and year.
